com.facebook.react.devsupport

Class DevSupportManagerFactory

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.facebook.react.devsupport.DevSupportManagerFactory

  • public class DevSupportManagerFactory
extends java.lang.Object
    A simple factory that creates instances of DevSupportManager implementations. Uses reflection to create DevSupportManagerImpl if it exists. This allows ProGuard to strip that class and its dependencies in release builds. If the class isn't found, DisabledDevSupportManager is returned instead.
